To automatically display the value of a variable "var" or register "reg"
after each stepping command:

display var
   or
display/fmt var
   or
display $reg

Examples:

display avar
display/x aptrvar
display $edx

To show all autodisplayed expressions by their index numbers:

info display

To stop displaying an item, delete it from the list by its display index number:

undisplay indexnum


Reference:  http://ftp.gnu.org/old-gnu/Manuals/gdb/html_node/gdb_56.html
